text: The Irawaddy frog or unknown copper-backed frog ("Hylarana" margariana) is a frog from Myanmar. Scientists are not sure which genus this frog should be in. That is why they write "Hylarana" in quotation marks instead of just Hylarana margariana. ==References== Category:Frogs of Asia Category:IUCN Red List data deficient species
title: Irawaddy frog
